**Eclipse Mining Consortium** is a [[mining pool|Pooled_mining]] with server locations in the US and EU. It is run by Josh Zerlan.

This pool pays out using a [[double geometric|Comparison_of_mining_pools]] share reward system. It also offers simultaneous [[merged mining|Alternative_chain]] of BTC and [[NMC]].

The service was first available on June 13, 2011 (1.1).

The [[coinbase]] signature for this pool is: "EMC" (1.2).

##Reward distribution

* Double Geometric Scoring: 0% fee.

